England University Staffs Plan One-Day Strike, Independent Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-03-21T19:14:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/england-university-staffs-plan-one-day-strike-independent-says.html
Thousands of academics at 47
universities and colleges across  England  will hold a 24-hour
strike tomorrow to protest against changes to their pension
program that will raise their  retirement age , increase their
contributions and end a final-salary  pension plan , the
Independent reported, citing Sally Hunt, general secretary of
the University and College Union.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  